data.description: Gorgeously maintained three bedroom brick home in east Wichita! This home boasts beautiful wood floors throughout, updated bathroom and cozy fireplace in the living room. Newer water heater, and main water line. New furnace and AC in the last 5 years. It sits on a large, nice corner lot with great shade. Close to a variety of restaurants and shopping. Schedule your private showing today!
